Font_FutureFont  (&4008C)
#Parent Font_
<=	R0 =	font handle
	R1 =	background colour
	R2 =	foreground colour
	R3 =	<foreground colour offset=>font_paint2>

This SWI returns what the state after the next call to <Font_Paint> would be. You must first have called <Font_StringWidth>.
